"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1638325006","stars":2213,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":770,"parent_node_name":"work"},"member":{"username":"BlackFri","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/44988fa6a9a9bc73d259bed42740c908?s=24&d=retro","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/BlackFri","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1627026316,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/44988fa6a9a9bc73d259bed42740c908?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/44988fa6a9a9bc73d259bed42740c908?s=24&d=retro","location":null,"btc":null,"id":551628},"last_reply_by":"360kabasiji","last_touched":1638541528,"title":"毕业两年半的朋友们还有没实现经济独立的吗","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/819698","created":1638493848,"deleted":0,"content":"很惭愧，还没有，一度怀疑自己的智商","content_rendered":"很惭愧，还没有，一度怀疑自己的智商","last_modified":1638493848,"replies":77,"id":819698},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1635654575","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1635654575","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":46528,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1635654575","stars":7609,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"username":"villivateur","website":"https://www.vvzero.com/","github":"","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/233d/26cb/273091_mini.png?m=1635395897","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/villivateur","tagline":"嵌入式物联网全栈系统工程师","twitter":"","created":1512652845,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/233d/26cb/273091_mini.png?m=1635395897","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/233d/26cb/273091_mini.png?m=1635395897","location":"","btc":"","id":273091},"last_reply_by":"bzj","last_touched":1638549334,"title":"公司从 SVN 切换到 Git 的那些坑","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/819771","created":1638509355,"deleted":0,"content":"为了实现代码检视（ Pull Request ）这个功能，公司从 SVN 切换到了 Git ，但是不少人遇到了下面的问题：\r\n\r\n1. 没有理解 Git 的工作区、暂存区、仓库区、远端之间的关系，用 SVN 的思维去使用 Git ，比如会通过删除工作区文件、再拉取代码这种方式来回退代码。\r\n2. 在修改工作区文件后，没有 commit 或者 stash ，就 pull 代码，导致提示冲突，因为不熟练所以不知道如何解决。\r\n3. 之前 SVN 仓库中有很多需要经常修改的大二进制文件，初期迁移的时候没有用 LFS 管理，导致 Git 仓库庞大，clone 要花很长时间。\r\n4. 使用 LFS 后，因为各个用户终端配置不一样，可能有的人没有装 LFS ，提交后，其他人再 pull ，会出现很多奇怪的问题。\r\n\r\n感觉从 SVN 切换到 Git ，还是要慎重，至少要培训熟练。","content_rendered":"<p>为了实现代码检视（ Pull Request ）这个功能，公司从 SVN 切换到了 Git ，但是不少人遇到了下面的问题：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>没有理解 Git 的工作区、暂存区、仓库区、远端之间的关系，用 SVN 的思维去使用 Git ，比如会通过删除工作区文件、再拉取代码这种方式来回退代码。</li>\n<li>在修改工作区文件后，没有 commit 或者 stash ，就 pull 代码，导致提示冲突，因为不熟练所以不知道如何解决。</li>\n<li>之前 SVN 仓库中有很多需要经常修改的大二进制文件，初期迁移的时候没有用 LFS 管理，导致 Git 仓库庞大，clone 要花很长时间。</li>\n<li>使用 LFS 后，因为各个用户终端配置不一样，可能有的人没有装 LFS ，提交后，其他人再 pull ，会出现很多奇怪的问题。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>感觉从 SVN 切换到 Git ，还是要慎重，至少要培训熟练。</p>\n","last_modified":1638509355,"replies":57,"id":819771},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1629391403","name":"create","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1629391403","title":"分享创造","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","topics":16984,"footer":"","header":"欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！","title_alternative":"Create","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1629391403","stars":4124,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":17,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"username":"viewweiwu","website":"","github":"viewweiwu","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3317/c0a5/301659_mini.png?m=1638447206","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/viewweiwu","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1521515106,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3317/c0a5/301659_mini.png?m=1638447206","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3317/c0a5/301659_mini.png?m=1638447206","location":"","btc":"","id":301659},"last_reply_